óŸRarchive/external_nushell_repo_backup/nushell.github.io/blog/2024-07-27-twin0257.mdŸ@e779420a0d80f230ec991a21485f18b91319826a03d414714f5244f8a7c44b12πThis week in Nushell #257ë≠Documentation⁄•devyn 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell.github.io/pull/1484] added an example for the new CallDecl engine call
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell.github.io/pull/1483] updated the 
``CustomValue``
 usage example
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell.github.io/pull/1475] abbreviated the output in an example in dataframes to avoid a typo false positive
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell.github.io/pull/1474] worked on the release notes for 0.96.0
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell.github.io/pull/1473] added 
``FindDecl``
 and 
``CallDecl``
 engine calls to the plugin protocol reference
.
sinisa-szabo 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell.github.io/pull/1482] updated 00_flow_control_overview.md
.
IanManske 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell.github.io/pull/1481] removed unnecessary ignore in typos config
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell.github.io/pull/1470] replaced 
``group``
 with 
``chunks``
 in the docs
.
hustcer 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell.github.io/pull/1480] refreshed command docs for Nu v0.96.0
.
NotTheDr01ds 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell.github.io/pull/1478] updated and fixed Cookbook Tables
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell.github.io/pull/1476] provided updates for 0.96 $in improvements
.
ayax79 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell.github.io/pull/1457] created release notes for 
``0.96.0``
.
