óŸRarchive/external_nushell_repo_backup/nushell.github.io/blog/2024-07-27-twin0257.mdŸ@d37868a5c8f01a742ebd46e5c0e6dce6f8ee8f953840b54607e9c50f58311160πThis week in Nushell #257ë™Nu_Scripts⁄˜NotTheDr01ds 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nu_scripts/pull/918] updated themes preview to use 
``chunks``
 instead of the deprecated 
``group``
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nu_scripts/pull/911] fixed cell-path in themes
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nu_scripts/pull/909] updated theme preview scripts and screenshots
.
christoph-blessing 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nu_scripts/pull/917] fixed incorrect docker commands
.
lizclipse 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nu_scripts/pull/916] fixed sys usage
.
ayax79 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nu_scripts/pull/915] fixed the ordering and added nu-drive-value for nu_release.nu
.
devyn 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nu_scripts/pull/914] added more notes about transferring ownership during release
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nu_scripts/pull/913] moved notes for plugin developers to the top level in release notes
.
sadguitarius 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nu_scripts/pull/910] added silent option to nu_msvs
.
AucaCoyan 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nu_scripts/pull/908] fixed 
``scope commands``
 call and columns
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nu_scripts/pull/801] provided parser fixes
.
OJarrisonn 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nu_scripts/pull/907] fixed catppuccin themes declared as 
``const``
 inside a record
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nu_scripts/pull/906] updated nu-complete for git ref and git files-and-ref to use nu-complete git switch
.
amtoine 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nu_scripts/pull/905] worked on the 
``nu-themes``
 make script
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nu_scripts/pull/901] bumped the 
``nu-hooks``
 package to 
``0.2.0``
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nu_scripts/pull/875] proposed an RFC to add a command to help parse arguments in scripts
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nu_scripts/pull/874] added 
``ways-to-add-up-to``
 to the "math" module
.
Okdro 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nu_scripts/pull/898] added git grep completions
.
